Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.07,0:00:16.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭 不是那樣的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.33,0:00:20.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的啦 你真的是胸部變大了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.54,0:00:22.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好惡心啊 不過...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.46,0:00:26.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死......
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.59,0:00:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別留下你們劣性的基因
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.63,0:00:30.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發春的淫獸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.63,0:00:32.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死去死
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.28,0:00:34.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是迷唇姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.28,0:00:34.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs27}注釋：口袋妖怪的一種
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.87,0:00:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是 女人真的是笨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.32,0:00:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是很像啊 嘴唇那麼厚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.62,0:00:43.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是這個理由的話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.85,0:00:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珠算學校的老爺爺也是迷唇姐了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.69,0:00:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.88,0:00:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.37,0:00:57.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.48,0:01:02.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏日的猛獸來勢洶洶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.44,0:01:06.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太狡猾了 面麻也要吃鹽拉面
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.02,0:01:10.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 雞蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.48,0:01:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻最喜歡雞蛋湯了 雞蛋湯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.58,0:01:22.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雞蛋要凝固了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.58,0:01:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把雞蛋攪拌開 攪拌開 攪拌開
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.62,0:01:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 拉面？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.92,0:01:32.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔 打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.77,0:01:32.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯嘛 仁太 給我也做一份吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.28,0:01:36.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.35,0:01:37.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 可以
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.74,0:01:39.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 真可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.49,0:01:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給叔叔做卻不給面麻做麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.05,0:01:43.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說可不可以不要什麼都說可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.30,0:01:46.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這是個好詞啊 什麼都能套上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.88,0:01:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是叔叔也說面麻很可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.28,0:01:49.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般都不用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.20,0:01:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雞蛋要什麼樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.16,0:01:52.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來個荷包蛋 不要絞碎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.33,0:01:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.62,0:01:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔也是這樣 偏心 偏心 偏心中年人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.51,0:01:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.62,0:02:01.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電視 電視
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.78,0:02:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.12,0:02:04.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貓咪好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.45,0:02:09.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸和平時一樣 這麼看來果然是...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.65,0:02:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.29,0:02:13.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.51,0:02:17.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.38,0:02:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡椒 胡椒 胡椒 好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.48,0:02:26.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻也要吃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.49,0:02:27.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.82,0:02:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.03,0:02:33.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筷子在哪裡 筷子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.63,0:02:33.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.50,0:02:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 在家裡熱得中暑了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.99,0:02:44.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然可愛 但是糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.34,0:02:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.23,0:02:49.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時的夏天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.73,0:02:59.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳 好危險的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.28,0:02:59.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.84,0:03:07.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 仁碳的這個是最大的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.16,0:03:09.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.01,0:03:12.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的 很厲害 很厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.38,0:03:15.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳真有型
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.45,0:03:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時的我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.67,0:03:19.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鶴見子 什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.64,0:03:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.62,0:03:25.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.61,0:03:30.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.13,0:03:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有個願望
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.80,0:05:21.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.76,0:05:27.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我確實是病了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.34,0:05:30.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這必定是我一直承受的壓力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.33,0:05:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與揮之不去的陰影
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.23,0:05:35.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為炎熱的夏天而成形
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.62,0:05:40.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至協同青春期的性衝動也席卷而來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.67,0:05:49.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.17,0:05:56.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就假設你是因為我的壓力具現化而出現在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.23,0:06:00.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 為什麼到現在才出現
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.37,0:06:06.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還是以成長後的姿態出現
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.49,0:06:10.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你這麼問我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.67,0:06:13.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.40,0:06:14.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.66,0:06:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.92,0:06:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概...我想是希望能夠實現願望吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.42,0:06:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.23,0:06:22.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,願望？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.94,0:06:24.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.38,0:06:26.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 那個是...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.36,0:06:29.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.88,0:06:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連願望都不知道是什麼 怎麼會實現啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.61,0:06:36.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 雖然是有點感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.80,0:06:38.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是真的其實是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.89,0:06:40.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼會知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.18,0:06:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,口水亂飛啊 真是好討厭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.97,0:06:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屏蔽掉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.99,0:06:47.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是夏日的猛獸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.24,0:06:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的壓力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.07,0:06:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的陰影
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.65,0:06:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.47,0:06:54.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先把那個什麼願望給我想起來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.45,0:06:56.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了對了 那個願望呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.90,0:06:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家不在一起的話就無法實現
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.89,0:07:02.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.19,0:07:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.88,0:07:05.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.55,0:07:07.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.26,0:07:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那個 門鈴在響
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.20,0:07:11.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是出現了要怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.59,0:07:13.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了 要乖乖的...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.38,0:07:17.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.84,0:07:21.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.86,0:07:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你冷靜一點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.58,0:07:26.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜？我並沒有在焦急啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.59,0:07:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不..沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.88,0:07:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺肩膀很重
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.99,0:07:38.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳴 看不到面麻嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.46,0:07:41.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 有什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.60,0:07:44.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.91,0:07:48.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師拜托我給你的暑假作業
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.76,0:07:49.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在才給我？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.06,0:07:52.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假什麼的 只剩下兩天了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.64,0:07:56.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和宿海不同 可是很忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.18,0:08:00.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然這樣的話 隨便找個地方扔掉不就好了 這東西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.22,0:08:03.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我不會再去那種傻學校了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.14,0:08:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿海來不來無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.00,0:08:10.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 你太不像樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.23,0:08:19.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.14,0:08:39.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳你個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.81,0:08:43.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼沒有拜托小鳴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.73,0:08:47.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起來實現願望吧 小鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.81,0:08:49.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事先說明
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.52,0:08:54.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要稱她小鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.45,0:08:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫安城或者鳴子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.70,0:08:59.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 小鳴就是小鳴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.77,0:09:04.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對大家都很溫柔 有好多漫畫和遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.22,0:09:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都說了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.77,0:09:10.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她已經不是那時的小鳴了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.47,0:09:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算去拜托那個臭女人 她也不會幫忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.04,0:09:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臭女人？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.75,0:09:18.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是蠢女人的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.36,0:09:20.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 和她已經不是朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.91,0:09:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.07,0:09:28.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 討厭說小鳴壞話的仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.63,0:09:29.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.77,0:09:34.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起去小鳴那裡 去拜托她吧 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.86,0:09:38.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.14,0:09:40.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.63,0:09:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂的那個願望說給安城聽的話 你會理解的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.96,0:09:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不僅是安城 所有的一切都改變了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.75,0:09:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳 還沒有好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.73,0:10:01.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了來了來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.54,0:10:08.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帽子和眼鏡?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.42,0:10:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.08,0:10:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.32,0:10:12.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.59,0:10:16.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,買東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.62,0:10:17.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.47,0:10:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.30,0:10:20.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.77,0:10:21.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.92,0:10:32.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.85,0:10:33.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.40,0:10:35.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好怪的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.79,0:10:38.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 臉上有吃拉面的蔥的痕迹 Honey
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.73,0:10:39.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.00,0:10:46.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.68,0:10:52.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.45,0:10:58.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳴的家不在這個方向
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.25,0:11:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便散步一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.71,0:11:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡以前是bombom吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.31,0:11:08.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在成了WcDonald了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.44,0:11:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害 不過面麻還是更喜歡...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.65,0:11:12.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同校的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.87,0:11:13.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.15,0:11:15.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是外星人會出來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.79,0:11:18.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有使用雙節棍的女人在學校打架的那個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.76,0:11:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.78,0:11:22.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是朋友麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.52,0:11:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.73,0:11:30.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊 被大媽破壞了心情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.12,0:11:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰也不會在意我的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.13,0:11:36.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安城也不是說了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.57,0:11:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這種人無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.29,0:11:47.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏天的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.66,0:11:50.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還是老樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.71,0:11:52.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.94,0:11:56.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理所當然啊 只是幻影而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.79,0:12:02.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實現...願望麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.63,0:12:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然這一定是我對面麻的...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.04,0:12:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.43,0:12:13.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.21,0:12:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼 很危險的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.51,0:12:22.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.02,0:12:27.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳 小面麻她...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.41,0:12:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.19,0:12:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.47,0:12:52.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.22,0:12:56.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼疼疼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.11,0:13:02.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿海 你在做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.06,0:13:07.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第1話 超和平克星
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.57,0:13:18.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 鳴子 你去小仁的家了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.15,0:13:19.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敲門
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.44,0:13:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 我沒有嗎 算了 還有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.54,0:13:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順道看了一下而已 這個應該跟媽媽你沒關系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.54,0:13:30.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有啊 我還想讓你帶點包子去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.20,0:13:33.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己帶去不就好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.12,0:13:35.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 青春期 青春期
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.45,0:13:37.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.19,0:13:45.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不像樣的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.65,0:13:48.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.68,0:13:54.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛從暑假講習那邊回來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.76,0:13:56.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟是新學校
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.93,0:14:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我應該穿高中校服的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.53,0:14:02.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.57,0:14:03.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿海？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.34,0:14:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.84,0:14:08.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 我先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.67,0:14:09.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.42,0:14:16.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是雪集和鶴子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.29,0:14:19.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.19,0:14:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不是 是面麻她 呃 不是 是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.07,0:14:26.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你提面麻做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.49,0:14:31.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到現在還在說這話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.27,0:14:34.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.87,0:14:35.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽說了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.70,0:14:36.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.88,0:14:40.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直沒去上學是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.31,0:14:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考試失敗 進入了一個垃圾學校
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.94,0:14:48.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連學校都不去一股勁叫本間芽衣子的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.50,0:14:51.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的大腦是不是壞掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.66,0:14:56.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.92,0:14:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集是大白癡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.38,0:15:05.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 你熱血什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.33,0:15:10.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一提到本間芽依子就像換了一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.12,0:15:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不也是這樣嗎 雪集君
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.79,0:15:16.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.32,0:15:20.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是可憐的家夥 只有臉長得帥而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.22,0:15:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很聰明的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.90,0:15:23.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.59,0:15:29.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.68,0:15:31.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.85,0:15:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.86,0:15:43.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣你總該明白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.72,0:15:46.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都變了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.96,0:15:52.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 變化最大的應該是我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.87,0:15:54.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳  那個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.10,0:15:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請饒了我的應激反應吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.46,0:16:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有你在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.20,0:16:05.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會想起 就會想起不開心的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.76,0:16:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓自己變得急躁起來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.25,0:16:17.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.89,0:16:32.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時 那時的夏天 不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.70,0:16:40.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 決定了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.25,0:16:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.75,0:16:45.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是超和平克星
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.17,0:16:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 太帥了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.18,0:16:50.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克星是？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.78,0:16:52.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貌似是指厲害的家夥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.47,0:16:55.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要保護和平
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.20,0:16:55.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太帥了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.07,0:16:56.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡的和平？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.66,0:17:00.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有地方的各種和平
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.84,0:17:04.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說仁碳是老大
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.22,0:17:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.65,0:17:09.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都圍繞著我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.13,0:17:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 即便那天也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.32,0:17:21.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.78,0:17:26.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡面麻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.09,0:17:29.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.08,0:17:33.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.40,0:17:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就誠實的回答吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.49,0:17:38.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們超和平克星是不能有事隱瞞的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.43,0:17:39.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.59,0:17:42.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說啊 說啊 說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.64,0:17:44.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 是不行的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.64,0:17:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說啊 說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.02,0:17:52.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰 誰會對這醜女
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.67,0:17:58.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以為她會哭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.49,0:18:01.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為面麻是哭泣蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.87,0:18:03.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.60,0:18:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.51,0:18:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.99,0:18:19.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 你回來了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.36,0:18:23.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先去趟你媽媽那邊 把飯熱一下再吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.61,0:18:33.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個笑容深深揪住了我的心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.46,0:18:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原想明天再去道歉好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.76,0:18:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真難吃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.26,0:18:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那個明天
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.03,0:18:45.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永遠的都沒到來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.76,0:18:58.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咖喱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.15,0:19:05.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 門開了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.09,0:19:06.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你關掉嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.61,0:19:08.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聰君
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.03,0:19:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 長這麼大了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.58,0:19:15.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 滿頭白發
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.90,0:19:26.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.24,0:19:28.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經夠了 你老這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.98,0:19:30.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聰君
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.68,0:19:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次咖喱都要給姐姐一份 看著就難受
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.24,0:19:38.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這是你姐姐最喜歡吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.04,0:19:41.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了是不吃東西的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.52,0:19:43.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你別這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.12,0:19:51.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你姐姐缺根筋 說不定還不知自己已經死了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.02,0:19:53.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.65,0:20:00.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻對自己已經死掉的事情 還是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.48,0:20:04.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.11,0:20:06.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼知道 是杯子它自己
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.65,0:20:08.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是姐姐  （趕快收拾）
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.97,0:20:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切 又不是我做的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.08,0:20:16.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都什麼啊 臭老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.38,0:20:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂亮的將和平克星除掉的我們
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.00,0:20:29.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無意中都分開了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.81,0:20:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻最喜歡雞蛋湯了 雞蛋湯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.42,0:20:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家夥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.52,0:20:55.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 曾經很想要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.33,0:21:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家夥會去的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.52,0:21:16.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都很想要那個明天 那個跟面麻道歉的明天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.20,0:21:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.10,0:21:29.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的壓力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.22,0:21:33.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的陰影
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.75,0:21:43.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我一定是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.36,0:21:48.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了向面麻道歉所以制造出了這個面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.00,0:21:51.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以再這樣下去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.86,0:22:07.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.87,0:22:17.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.03,0:22:23.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也太...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.60,0:22:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 正是這種反差才是浪漫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.08,0:22:31.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 是仁碳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.20,0:22:33.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波波
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.65,0:22:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們在這裡刻上名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.22,0:22:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超怎麼寫？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.97,0:22:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.39,0:22:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 左邊一個走
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.27,0:22:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走怎麼寫？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.16,0:22:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼在這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.93,0:22:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs25}（超和平Busters）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.57,0:22:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一天 停止于這裡的時間又開始轉動
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.94,0:22:59.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻應該回哪裡才好呢？
