Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.97,0:21:50.91,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}在空中綻放的美麗煙火
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.05,0:21:52.97,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}略微傷感
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.18,0:21:59.53,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}啊 微風同時間一起流逝
